# A configuration file for Imfit that specifies a Sersic, a FerrersBar2D and Exponential model for Au-18NoR #

ORIGINAL_SKY 68.15

X0      256.00      254,258
Y0      256.00      254,258

FUNCTION Sersic
PA      90          fixed
ell     0.0         0,1
n       0.12        0,2
I_e     65
r_e     156

FUNCTION FerrersBar2D
PA      90          fixed
ell     0.7         0.3,0.8
c0      0.0         0,1
n       1.2         0,2
I_0     100         80,150
a_bar   94          70,120

FUNCTION Exponential
PA      180         fixed
ell     0.0         0,0.2
I_0     183
h       288

